'''Henock Trouillot''' (1923 - 1988) was a [[Haiti]]an historian, playwright, and novelist. He wrote historical and sociological books, such as:
* ''Historiographie d'Haïti'' (1954) * ''La Condition des Nègres Domestiques à Saint-Domingue'' (1955) * ''Economie et Finances de Saint-Domingue'' (1965) * ''La Vengeance du Mapou'' (1967) * ''Le Gouvernement du Roi Henri Christophe'' (1974)
He was the uncle of [[Michel-Rolph Trouillot]], the anthropologist and historical theorist.
